public social media account
looks pretty good.

36
00:02:15,662 --> 00:02:17,023
The number of fans is growing.

37
00:02:17,176 --> 00:02:18,808
The business operations
are keeping up too.

38
00:02:19,183 --> 00:02:20,262
However, print media

39
00:02:20,822 --> 00:02:21,743
doesn't do online sales.

40
00:02:22,743 --> 00:02:23,783
The sales performance is subpar.

41
