must be substantial.

56
00:02:52,023 --> 00:02:53,183
You must maintain its reputation.

57
00:02:55,862 --> 00:02:56,382
Understood.

58
00:02:56,620 --> 00:02:58,088
I'll head back
and organize the proposal.

59
00:02:58,542 --> 00:02:58,982
By the way,

60
00:02:59,288 --> 00:03:01,736
Liang Daiwen will be giving a seminar
about accessible designs tonight.

61
00:03:01,736 --> 00:03:02,584
