69
00:03:16,820 --> 00:03:18,968
We have to fulfill our social
obligations from time to time,

70
00:03:19,016 --> 00:03:19,420
am I right?

71
00:03:19,623 --> 00:03:21,303
Publicly supporting a seminar once

72
00:03:21,580 --> 00:03:22,936
doesn't mean we have selfish motives.

73
00:03:23,662 --> 00:03:24,102
Understood.

74
00:03:24,408 --> 00:03:25,288
Thank you, Ms. Zhang.

75
00:03:25,662 --> 00:03:26,702
You don't need to thank me.

76
00:03:27,064 --> 00:03:28,180
I did nothing to help you out.

77
00:03:30,063 --> 00:03:31,422
I've told Penny about this.

78
00:03:31,880 --> 00:03:33,340
Just do what you're supposed to do.

79
00:03:35,528 --> 00:03:36,500
For the branch publications,

80
