make you farther away from these people)

91
00:05:01,462 --> 00:05:02,142
Hello, everyone.

92
00:05:02,743 --> 00:05:03,543
Welcome to

93
00:05:03,576 --> 00:05:05,320
our accessibility product
promotional seminar.

94
00:05:05,416 --> 00:05:07,020
I'm Liang Daiwen,
the designer of the product.

95
00:05:08,222 --> 00:05:10,142
Before I begin,

96
00:05:10,423 --> 00:05:11,782
I have a question for you all.

97
00:05:12,782 --> 00:05:13,779
Among

98
00:05:13,780 --> 00:05:14,888
your friends, family members,

99
00:05:15,063 --> 00:05:15,983
and colleagues,

100
00:05:16,392 --> 00:05:17,700
are there any people with disabilities?

101
00:05:25,304 --> 00:05:26,420
According to my understanding,

102
00:05:27,063 --> 00:05:28,503
one out of seven people

103
00:05:28,822 --> 00:05:30,222
has disabilities.

104
00:05:31,183 --> 00:05:33,022
We might not notice their presence

105
00:05:33,303 --> 00:05:34,342
during our daily lives,

106
00:05:35,183 --> 00:05:35,743
however,

107
00:05:36,303 --> 00:05:37,222
just like us,

108
00:05:38,022 --> 00:05:39,943
they have the right
to fulfill their needs too.

109
00:05:41,462 --> 00:05:43,342
Now, I mainly focus on
accessibility design.

110
00:05:44,063 --> 00:05:45,582
I have a professional R&D team.

111
00:05:46,136 --> 00:05:48,540
I have gained a deeper understanding
of people with disabilities.

112
00:05:49,423 --> 00:05:50,222
I realized that...

113
00:05:51,222 --> 00:05:53,503
Director Peng planned to give you
some additional business ads

114
00:05:53,503 --> 00:05:54,423
in the later issues.

115
00:05:54,504 --> 00:05:56,072
Why didn't you reply
to his texts on WeChat?

116
00:05:59,224 --> 00:06:00,744
I'll definitely do it
if the ads are good.

117
00:06:01,222 --> 00:06:02,663
But I won't do something like this

118
00:06:02,820 --> 00:06:03,848
