125
00:06:19,222 --> 00:06:19,782
I remember you.

126
00:06:20,222 --> 00:06:21,462
You're Zhang Junjie's sweetheart.

127
00:06:23,103 --> 00:06:24,222
How is it?

128
00:06:24,382 --> 00:06:25,582
Has she given you a raise?

129
00:06:27,022 --> 00:06:27,582
Shut up.

130
00:06:28,152 --> 00:06:29,800
There are regulations
for a wage raise in Nextmonday.

131
00:06:29,800 --> 00:06:30,680
She's still inexperienced.

132
00:06:32,063 --> 00:06:34,582
The editor-in-chief doesn't even
have the right to demand a raise?

133
00:06:35,382 --> 00:06:36,022
Just look at them.

134
00:06:36,743 --> 00:06:37,943
I told you before.

135
00:06:37,980 --> 00:06:39,608
I said you could become
my business partner.

136
00:06:39,624 --> 00:06:40,808
But you weren't willing to do so.

137
00:06:42,063 --> 00:06:43,262
That old fox Roger

138
00:06:43,262 --> 00:06:44,543
