139
00:06:45,022 --> 00:06:45,983
How can you stand that?

140
00:06:47,262 --> 00:06:47,822
You're noisy.

141
00:06:48,543 --> 00:06:49,582
Shut up. Stop talking.

142
00:06:50,142 --> 00:06:51,423
I'll tell you in private.

143
00:06:52,303 --> 00:06:53,822
Now, Penny's reign

144
00:06:53,822 --> 00:06:54,943
is already over.

145
00:06:55,582 --> 00:06:57,262
