146
00:06:57,262 --> 00:06:58,543
and replace her with Gu Yi,

147
00:06:59,063 --> 00:06:59,582
I'm sure Roger

148
00:06:59,983 --> 00:07:01,342
won't raise any eyebrows.

149
00:07:02,984 --> 00:07:03,688
Sit down.

150
00:07:03,688 --> 00:07:04,380
What are you doing?

151
00:07:04,382 --> 00:07:05,582
I'm not done yet.

152
00:07:06,222 --> 00:07:06,943
Sorry about this.

153
00:07:07,623 --> 00:07:08,743
The people in the last row,

154
00:07:09,863 --> 00:07:10,743
