155
00:07:15,462 --> 00:07:16,303
Are you referring to me?

156
00:07:16,822 --> 00:07:17,663
That's right.

157
00:07:18,342 --> 00:07:20,142
Sorry. We'll stop talking.
Please continue.

158
00:07:22,303 --> 00:07:23,582
Please leave.

159
