Hey, you.

170
00:07:45,623 --> 00:07:48,022
Do you think you can achieve success

171
00:07:48,423 --> 00:07:49,543
with your accessible designs?

172
00:07:50,760 --> 00:07:52,020
You're getting ahead of yourself

173
00:07:52,022 --> 00:07:53,262
