174
00:07:53,368 --> 00:07:54,408
I'll say this one last time.

175
00:07:55,103 --> 00:07:55,983
Leave immediately.

176
00:08:31,260 --> 00:08:32,392
Sorry about that, everyone.

177
00:08:32,943 --> 00:08:33,663
Let's continue.

178
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:47,340
I'll get the car. I'll send you back.

179
00:08:48,742 --> 00:08:49,342
Gu Yi,

180
00:08:49,784 --> 00:08:51,060
follow me back and work overtime.

181
00:08:51,903 --> 00:08:52,943
Drive the car here.

182
00:09:00,822 --> 00:09:02,383
Do you need me to text Mr. Yu

183
00:09:02,383 --> 00:09:03,423
and tell him to pick you up?

184
00:09:07,896 --> 00:09:08,580
No need for that.

185
00:09:09,622 --> 00:09:10,063
Gu Yi,

186
00:09:10,822 --> 00:09:12,143
once I'm done with this program,

187
00:09:12,303 --> 00:09:13,099
I can be together

188
00:09:13,100 --> 00:09:14,392
with Yu Dule
without any worries.

189
00:09:15,383 --> 00:09:16,102
Just trust me.

190
00:09:16,303 --> 00:09:17,023
I know my own limits.

191
00:09:19,464 --> 00:09:20,220
I'll be going now.

192
00:09:33,920 --> 00:09:35,656
(Mr. Yu, grant me access
to Fuzzy's backend.)

193
00:09:35,702 --> 00:09:37,582
