200
00:10:02,462 --> 00:10:03,742
I'm not.

201
00:10:03,784 --> 00:10:05,170
Doing rough cuts
is a kind of job as well.

202
00:10:05,176 --> 00:10:06,616
There's nothing embarrassing about that.

203
00:10:09,143 --> 00:10:11,139
Are you in trouble lately?

204
00:10:11,140 --> 00:10:12,680
