216
00:10:35,702 --> 00:10:36,742
I'll stop messing with you.

217
00:10:37,063 --> 00:10:37,822
I'll make a move first.

218
00:10:37,982 --> 00:10:38,943
You should leave early too.

219
00:10:39,300 --> 00:10:40,120
Since they're rough cuts,

220
00:10:40,143 --> 00:10:40,903
