this psychological issue may seem

235
00:13:18,822 --> 00:13:19,543
insignificant,

236
00:13:20,742 --> 00:13:22,102
but to his partner,

237
00:13:23,336 --> 00:13:25,240
he'll show you the cold shoulder
like what he did today

238
00:13:25,256 --> 00:13:26,840
on numerous occasions in the future.

239
00:13:27,222 --> 00:13:28,582
Are you sure you don't mind that?

240
00:13:32,102 --> 00:13:33,822
Liang Daiwen is very important to me.

241
00:13:34,783 --> 00:13:36,822
It doesn't make sense for me
to give up on him

242
00:13:37,263 --> 00:13:38,222
because of alexithymia.

243
00:13:41,064 --> 00:13:42,780
I've come up
with this week's theme for you.

244
00:13:43,352 --> 00:13:45,176
Finalize the schedule plan
within this week.

245
00:13:46,183 --> 00:13:47,102
You can't edit this video

246
00:13:47,663 --> 00:13:48,582
with your lousy laptop.

247
00:13:49,383 --> 00:13:50,582
Edit it with my computer.

248
00:13:52,020 --> 00:13:53,896
But you're not allowed
to touch the items on the desk.

249
00:13:55,222 --> 00:13:55,943
Thank you, Ms. Zhang.

250
00:14:07,183 --> 00:14:07,943
Here.

251
00:14:13,222 --> 00:14:13,663
The ads

252
00:14:13,663 --> 00:14:14,939
were very effective.

253
00:14:14,940 --> 00:14:16,022
It's all thanks to Director Peng.

254
00:14:16,023 --> 00:14:16,862
You were outstanding.

255
00:14:17,183 --> 00:14:17,622
And,

256
00:14:17,742 --> 00:14:18,702
the female lead beside him

257
00:14:18,822 --> 00:14:19,663
was outstanding too.

258
00:14:19,663 --> 00:14:19,939
Yes.

259
00:14:19,940 --> 00:14:21,288
Director Peng,
thank you for your support.

260
00:14:21,303 --> 00:14:22,423
Good job, everyone.

