00:14:24,663 --> 00:14:25,063
Let's eat.

265
00:14:26,303 --> 00:14:26,742
Wenda.

266
00:14:27,183 --> 00:14:27,663
Xingxin.

267
00:14:30,063 --> 00:14:30,943
You're late.

268
00:14:31,222 --> 00:14:31,903
Sorry about that.

269
00:14:31,903 --> 00:14:32,783
Mr. Liu, I'm truly sorry.

270
00:14:32,783 --> 00:14:33,379
Come.

271
00:14:33,380 --> 00:14:34,760
